[
    {
        "text": "The European Space Agency has chosen the British paralympic sprinter, John McFall,...",
        "startTime": 799,
        "endTime": 6645,
        "slowStartTime": 1348,
        "slowEndTime": 10193
    },
    {
        "text": "...as the first astronaut with a disability to join the space training team.",
        "startTime": 7051,
        "endTime": 11143,
        "slowStartTime": 10726,
        "slowEndTime": 16939
    },
    {
        "text": "He'll work with designers and engineers to see if it's possible for him to go into space.",
        "startTime": 11515,
        "endTime": 16014,
        "slowStartTime": 17422,
        "slowEndTime": 24246
    },
    {
        "text": "Our science editor, Rebecca Morelle, reports.",
        "startTime": 16331,
        "endTime": 18981,
        "slowStartTime": 24646,
        "slowEndTime": 28697
    },
    {
        "text": "It's the job of dreams with an office that's got spectacular views...",
        "startTime": 20436,
        "endTime": 24661,
        "slowStartTime": 30804,
        "slowEndTime": 37217
    },
    {
        "text": "...offering an out of this world experience.",
        "startTime": 24915,
        "endTime": 27539,
        "slowStartTime": 37523,
        "slowEndTime": 41534
    },
    {
        "text": "Many would love to be an astronaut, but very few make the cut.",
        "startTime": 28049,
        "endTime": 31479,
        "slowStartTime": 42224,
        "slowEndTime": 47443
    },
    {
        "text": "Now in Paris, the European Space Agency has added...",
        "startTime": 33097,
        "endTime": 35945,
        "slowStartTime": 49796,
        "slowEndTime": 54142
    },
    {
        "text": "...some new names to the roll of honor.",
        "startTime": 36027,
        "endTime": 37937,
        "slowStartTime": 54191,
        "slowEndTime": 57131
    },
    {
        "text": "Selected from more than 22,000 applicants, this is the astronaut class of 2022.",
        "startTime": 38471,
        "endTime": 44675,
        "slowStartTime": 57857,
        "slowEndTime": 67237
    },
    {
        "text": "But for the first time ESA is widening its pool of talent...",
        "startTime": 46049,
        "endTime": 49477,
        "slowStartTime": 69224,
        "slowEndTime": 74441
    },
    {
        "text": "...by recruiting the first ever para-astronaut.",
        "startTime": 49667,
        "endTime": 52687,
        "slowStartTime": 74650,
        "slowEndTime": 79256
    },
    {
        "text": "I think being an amputee, being an astronaut was never really on my radar.",
        "startTime": 53298,
        "endTime": 58894,
        "slowStartTime": 80097,
        "slowEndTime": 88566
    },
    {
        "text": "John McFall is a paralympian sprinter.",
        "startTime": 59314,
        "endTime": 61679,
        "slowStartTime": 89121,
        "slowEndTime": 92743
    },
    {
        "text": "His right leg was amputated above the knee after a motorbike accident.",
        "startTime": 61987,
        "endTime": 66014,
        "slowStartTime": 93131,
        "slowEndTime": 99246
    },
    {
        "text": "He's been selected using exactly the same criteria as all European astronauts.",
        "startTime": 66261,
        "endTime": 71005,
        "slowStartTime": 99541,
        "slowEndTime": 106732
    },
    {
        "text": "The only difference is he has a disability.",
        "startTime": 71233,
        "endTime": 73231,
        "slowStartTime": 107000,
        "slowEndTime": 110072
    },
    {
        "text": "I thought I would have the skills and mix of skills and scientific background...",
        "startTime": 73418,
        "endTime": 77078,
        "slowStartTime": 110277,
        "slowEndTime": 115842
    },
    {
        "text": "...that I could really help them answer this very aspirational question...",
        "startTime": 77567,
        "endTime": 82258,
        "slowStartTime": 116500,
        "slowEndTime": 123612
    },
    {
        "text": "...of \"Can we get someone with a physical disability into space,...",
        "startTime": 82349,
        "endTime": 87122,
        "slowStartTime": 123674,
        "slowEndTime": 130908
    },
    {
        "text": "...to work in space safely?\"",
        "startTime": 87233,
        "endTime": 88432,
        "slowStartTime": 131000,
        "slowEndTime": 132873
    },
    {
        "text": "All astronauts have to undergo rigorous training.",
        "startTime": 89114,
        "endTime": 91857,
        "slowStartTime": 133821,
        "slowEndTime": 138011
    },
    {
        "text": "Part of John's job will be to test how the kits like spacesuits and spacecraft...",
        "startTime": 92287,
        "endTime": 96764,
        "slowStartTime": 138580,
        "slowEndTime": 145371
    },
    {
        "text": "...need to be adapted.",
        "startTime": 96846,
        "endTime": 97873,
        "slowStartTime": 145419,
        "slowEndTime": 147035
    },
    {
        "text": "His selection doesn't mean he'll definitely get to go into space,...",
        "startTime": 98389,
        "endTime": 101399,
        "slowStartTime": 147734,
        "slowEndTime": 152323
    },
    {
        "text": "...but he still wants to pave the way to make it happen.",
        "startTime": 101613,
        "endTime": 103992,
        "slowStartTime": 152569,
        "slowEndTime": 156213
    }
]